reviewText:
I love the action the plot and the supernatural
elements in the movies.
The supernatural elements could have been
more intense in the storylines,but they were
still good movies.
ok films made on a budget
These three movies are on a single sided disc. They were described as being on 3 discs.  I did not watch the movies.
If you like good B movies you can't beat all three of these for the price and you get a whole night worth of B movie bliss to watch
